   <head>Epigrammi - IV. Ad Federicum.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Litibus abstinui semper; mihi testis Apollo est,</l>
     <l n="2">Et Musae, et studiis otia grata meis.</l>
     <l n="3">Nunc me nescio quis per tristia jurgia versat</l>
     <l n="4">Scotius, et rauci cogit ad arma fori.</l>
     <l n="5">Es fateor magnus pulsis, Rex inclyte, Gallis.</l>
     <l n="6">Pelle etiam Scotos, et mihi major eris.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
